This take is good enough, right?

43
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,600
Not really, we have to do it again.

44
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:34,560
Xu Xiangdong.

45
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:36,200
Before you come down from above,

46
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:38,560
you should choose the moment

47
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:39,680
she yells

48
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:41,080
in extreme fear, right?

49
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:42,320
You have to get the moment.

50
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:43,680
Bunny.

51
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,120
You can't just scream.

52
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:46,080
You must feel fear

53
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:47,240
from within.

54
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:48,240
Let the audience

55
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,600
see that fear inside you.

56
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:51,240
Like, to dilate pupils.

57
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,320
Do you get it?

58
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:55,080
No, I mean...

59
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:56,800
To dilate pupils.

60
00:03:58,240 --> 00:04:00,240
Not enough. More.

61
00:04:01,320 --> 00:04:02,320
That's not it.

62
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:03,320
Why don't you get it?

63
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:06,080
Director, show me how to dilate pupils.

64
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:07,720
Fine, forget it.

65
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,440
Anyway, you're wearing contacts.

66
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:10,680
Just mind your expression.

67
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:11,800
Like you're in extreme fear.

68
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:12,800
In extreme fear, okay?

69
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,800
You know what I mean.

70
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:16,400
Xiao Rang.

71
00:04:16,400 --> 00:04:18,080
What's wrong with me? I was quite well.

72
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:19,600
No way.

73
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:21,600
When he falls down,
your camera should follow.

74
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,680
Why did you stand still?

75
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:23,800
How am I supposed to do it?

76
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:24,960
What about the actress?

77
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:26,600
Can't you just edit it?

78
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:27,520
What?

79
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,240
I've told you

80
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:29,680
I am a director pursuing perfection.

81
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:30,960
We are filming a horror film.

82
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:33,040
That immersive feeling
will be gone with the edit.

83
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:33,720
Oh, my.

84
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:34,800
What immersive feeling?

85
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,440
You just don't know how to film.

86
00:04:36,440 --> 00:04:37,080
Fine.

87
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:38,440
Film it your way.

88
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:39,080
Let's see if...

89
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:40,320
What? Again?

90
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:41,040
No more.

91
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,520
This is the fifth take. No more.

92
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:43,600
You can't direct,

93
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,720
and you can't film.

94
00:04:44,880 --> 00:04:46,600
So you're just fooling me around, right?

95
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,600
Who can't film?

96
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,160
You.

97
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:48,720
You do it.

98
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,800
Look at my makeup.

99
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,320
I quit.

100
00:04:50,320 --> 00:04:51,440
Can you take the shot?

101
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:52,880
My makeup is wasted.

102
00:04:52,880 --> 00:04:54,080
You think you look good?

103
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,520
Does he look good?

104
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:56,520
Take a look.

105
00:04:56,520 --> 00:04:57,680
Give him a close-up.

106
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:59,720
What's with me?

107
00:05:01,520 --> 00:05:02,320
What's with her?

108
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:07,080
What's with her?

109
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:09,960
Dancing?

110
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:12,320
Well, if we can't do it today,

111
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:13,520
maybe tomorrow.

112
00:05:13,520 --> 00:05:14,400
Don't get worked up.

113
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:19,400
All of you have to film today.

114
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:29,880
- Shut the door.
- Shut it.

115
00:05:30,144 --> 00:05:30,680
Shut it.

116
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:31,520
Let's go. Move.

117
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,240
Why do you make a film?

118
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:44,160
Like you don't care about your life.

119
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:45,720
I just don't care about my life.

120
