Disgusting.

135
00:06:34,320 --> 00:06:35,360
Are you Xiao Rang?

136
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,000
I am.

137
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:36,800
Are you Chen Meixi?

138
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:37,640
Yes.

139
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,800
Shall we talk somewhere else?

140
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:42,800
Alright.

141
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:48,920
How is it?

142
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,520
I look similar to the photo, right?

143
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:51,720
Well, right.

144
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:52,480
Very good.

145
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:56,200
Right, roses,

146
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:56,920
the token.

147
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:58,440
Thank you, I like them very much.

148
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:00,920
Right, my token.

149
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:08,080
How is it? Looks good, right?

150
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:13,080
Yes.

151
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:17,320
Are you hungry?

152
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:19,880
Shall we have a meal first?

153
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:20,440
Alright.

154
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:33,520
Film it from the bottom up
to find the backlight.

155
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:36,200
No, let's try again.

156
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,200
Go up.

157
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,080
This person is sick.

158
00:07:40,080 --> 00:07:40,640
Exactly.

159
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:41,920
The toilet is nearby.

160
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,480
Move up.

161
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,360
Okay.

162
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:53,760
Recognize me?

163
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,520
You are...

164
00:07:55,760 --> 00:07:56,920
It doesn't matter.

165
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:58,320
I've been observing you.

166
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:00,320
Me?

167
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:02,200
Like filming short videos?

168
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:07,200
Not exactly,
I'm thinking of making a film.

169
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:10,200
Exactly, I can tell

170
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:11,080
you are a director.

171
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:12,480
You can tell that?

172
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:13,640
Moreover,

173
00:08:13,640 --> 00:08:14,640
I can tell

174
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:15,440
you have potential

175
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:18,360
to make a great film.

176
00:08:19,080 --> 00:08:20,080
Really?

177
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:20,920
Really.

178
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:23,920
Just from how you shot videos
with your phone.

179
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:25,200
The angle and adjustment.

180
00:08:25,200 --> 00:08:26,440
I can imagine

181
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:28,440
the serious look you have

182
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:30,320
sitting behind the monitor.

183
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:32,040
Thank you.

184
00:08:35,040 --> 00:08:37,480
Let me introduce myself.

185
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:39,440
I'm a director scout

186
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:41,120
who specializes in finding new directors

187
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,320
like you.

188
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,320
Director scout?

189
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:47,320
I've never heard of it before.

190
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:49,200
Because you haven't
entered the industry.

191
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:51,400
There are many new directors
like you nowadays.

192
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:53,200
What do you need? A chance.

193
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:55,880
That's why you need
talent scouts like us

194
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:57,120
to go discover you,

195
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,560
then you'll have the chance...

196
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,080
Right?

197
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,880
That's great.

198
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:03,000
T-Thank you.

199
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:05,400
Alright then, see you.

200
00:09:05,560 --> 00:09:06,640
Okay. Pleased to meet you.

201
00:09:06,640 --> 00:09:07,760
See you.

202
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:08,640
Thank you.

203
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:13,640
Then I'm leaving.

204
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:14,368
You...

205
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:16,880
Sorry.

206
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:18,640
I didn't get your contact yet.

207
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:20,096
Here.

208
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:21,632
- Okay.
- My business card.

209
00:09:21,632 --> 00:09:22,200
Okay.

210
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:22,760
Keep it well.

211
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:23,760
I know you can do it.

212
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:25,440
Alright, goodbye.

213
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:26,200
Goodbye.

214
00:09:28,435 --> 00:09:29,216
(Xu Xiangdong)

215
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,320
Xu Xiangdong.

216
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:34,120
Xu Xiangdong?

217
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,320
The decor

218
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:37,880
of this store seems ordinary,

219
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,320
but it holds hidden surprises.

220
00:09:39,560 --> 00:09:41,640
This is my Happy Hometown, do you know?

221
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:43,120
If it weren't a bit pricey,

222
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,320
I'd eat here every day.

223
00:09:44,760 --> 00:09:45,376
Really?

224
00:09:45,376 --> 00:09:45,880
Really.

225
00:09:45,880 --> 00:09:47,000
Then I must try it out.

226
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,000
You're sure to love it.

227
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:49,200
Waitress.

228
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:53,840
Here you are.

229
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:54,640
Here I am.

230
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:55,520
Haven't come in days,

231
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:56,440
I've been craving it.

232
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:58,200
Your girlfriend?

233
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:02,840
My good friend.

234
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:03,880
Let's see what to eat.

235
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:05,320
I'll pass.

236
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:06,200
You take a look.

237
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:08,880
I'll have ten silkworm chrysalises,
ten grasshoppers,

238
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:09,440
two kidneys,

239
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,440
and stinky tofu.

240
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,200
No problem.

241
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:13,320
Just order whatever you like.

242
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,440
It's okay. I'm on a diet,

243
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:16,520
so I won't eat for now.

244
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:20,760
Is there that new deep-fried scorpion
on the menu?

245
00:10:20,880 --> 00:10:21,440
Yes.

246
00:10:21,640 --> 00:10:22,560
Do you want to try it?

247
00:10:22,560 --> 00:10:23,440
It's really tasty.

248
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:26,760
It's fine. I'll take it step by step.

249
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:27,904
Alright, that's all.

250
00:10:27,904 --> 00:10:28,440
Okay.

251
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,080
Please hurry up.

252
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,120
No problem.

253
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:34,440
I think you don't need to lose weight.

254
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:35,440
You're not fat.

255
00:10:35,760 --> 00:10:37,560
Besides, the silkworm chrysalis

256
00:10:37,560 --> 00:10:39,120
is a high-protein food,

257
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:40,280
particularly good for girls.

258
00:10:40,760 --> 00:10:42,000
It won't make much difference

259
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,080
by not eating one meal.

260
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:48,000
All are served.

261
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:48,560
Thank you.

262
00:10:48,560 --> 00:10:49,640
Tell me if you need more.

263
00:10:49,640 --> 00:10:50,280
- Alright.
- Enjoy.

264
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:50,840
Alright.

265
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:53,120
You first.

266
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,440
- It's fine, you first.
- Or it'll get cold.

267
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:58,400
I have to go to the restroom.

268
00:10:59,520 --> 00:11:00,760
Okay, I'll wait for you.

269
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:10,080
I can't start eating
before my guest does.

270
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:32,760
You are back early.

271
00:11:32,880 --> 00:11:34,080
Why are you primping here?

272
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:35,320
I'm leaving right away.

273
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:40,080
Right.

274
00:11:40,640 --> 00:11:42,080
Help me with the roll call.

275
00:11:42,760 --> 00:11:43,960
No way.

276
00:11:45,640 --> 00:11:46,880
I'll treat you to a meal.

277
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:13,520
Why are you here?

278
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:14,520
I...

279
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,760
Just passing by.

280
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:22,200
Since I'm already here,

281
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:24,200
why don't you buy me a coffee?

282
00:12:24,760 --> 00:12:26,760
I'll have that coconut latte.

283
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:27,640
Sure.

284
00:12:35,379 --> 00:12:36,384
(China Merchants Bank Deposit Card,
Balance: 31 yuan)

285
00:12:37,555 --> 00:12:38,336
(Coconut Latte: 32)

286
00:12:38,419 --> 00:12:39,219
(Checkout)

287
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:42,200
Well,

288
00:12:43,280 --> 00:12:45,440
the coconut taro latte is also sweet.

289
00:12:45,760 --> 00:12:46,560
How about Americano?

290
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:50,080
I can't sleep if I drink Americano.

291
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:52,000
The coconut latte can be without sugar.

292
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:52,960
