00:27:41,440 --> 00:27:42,080
No more.

631
00:27:42,520 --> 00:27:43,920
Don't, you have to film.

632
00:27:43,920 --> 00:27:45,160
You could be a good director.

633
00:27:45,160 --> 00:27:46,000
